OL,3,CMet Police firearms officer accused of
OL,4,Cmurdering Chris Kaba named
OL,6,FUntil now the police officer was known
OL,7,Fby the code name "NX121", ITV News
OL,8,FSenior Correspondent Ronke Phillips
OL,9,Freports
OL,11,FThe firearms officer charged with the
OL,12,Fmurder of Chris Kaba in September 2022
OL,13,Fhas been named as Martyn Blake.
OL,15,FJudge Mark Lucraft KC said naming
OL,16,FBlake, 40, posed no real or immediate
OL,17,Frisk to his life or that of his
OL,18,Ffamily, and that it was normal
OL,19,Fpractice to do so.
