OL,6,FPolice officers said, he refused to
OL,7,Fget out of his vehicle, which was an
OL,8,FAudi officers believed was linked to a
OL,9,Ffirearms incident the previous day.
OL,11,FBlake shot him in the head once
OL,12,Fthrough the windscreen and Mr Kaba
OL,13,Fthen died of his injuries.
OL,15,FNo firearms were found in the car.
OL,17,FBlake was charged with murder in
OL,18,FSeptember 2023.
