OL,6,FIn response to the charge in
OL,7,FSeptember, up to 300 Metropolitan
OL,8,FPolice officers authorised to carry
OL,9,Ffirearms returned their permits to do
OL,10,Fso, over concerns about the decision
OL,11,Fto prosecute.
OL,13,FMore than 2,500 of the almost 34,000
OL,14,FMetropolitan Police officers are
OL,15,Flicensed to carry firearms.
OL,17,FBlake was referred to as "NX121" while
OL,18,Fcourt proceedings were underway.
