OL,6,FHaving originally been granted
OL,7,Fanonymity, Judge Mark Lucraft ruled
OL,8,Fthat NX121 would be named, two months
OL,9,Flater after originally planned.
OL,11,FMembers of Mr Kaba's family were in
OL,12,Fcourt at the Old Bailey on Friday as
OL,13,Fthe officer was publicly named for the
OL,14,Ffirst time. Some left the courtroom in
OL,15,Ftears during the hearing.
OL,17,FCritics of the decision to name Blake
OL,18,Fsay it undermines police confidence in
OL,19,Ftheir ability to do their jobs.
